{"tid":1564422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去咗外國exchange可以做啲乜","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:46:05.000Z","uid":276694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"872415d37676a4268c9328e2038d8c6518797469","tid":1564422,"uid":276694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"求大家唔好屌小弟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟一年前已經報咗exchange<br />\n自己U基本上係將小弟掉咗去嗰邊U<br />\n所以冇得揀一定要過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就想趁呢個機會同外國嘅朋友仔講下香港嘅情況 <br />\n不過小弟英文唔好 唔知點同佢哋解釋<br />\n所以想大家俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我揼低大家好衰 但麻煩大家幫手推下諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個好對唔住大家嘅P牌仔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a493bf14e3cc1098e5bf310159a68fb103ec59","tid":1564422,"uid":251769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REHv0jX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREHv0jX.png&h=4961a981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSVp4MD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSVp4MD.jpg&h=3d25b08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvwgVTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvwgVTi.jpg&h=88868b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZxWVTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZxWVTj.png&h=651de955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8a608125754a8b4105499e41308fd9bbdb62a30","tid":1564422,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:15:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class